Interface PluginManager


  • public interface PluginManager
    The system for plugins management.
    插件管理系统。

    • Method Summary

      PluginFilter getPluginFilter()
      Returns currently installed plugin filter.
      返回当前安装的插件过滤器。

      Returns a list with the information about installed plugins.
      返回包含有关已安装插件的信息的列表。

    • Method Detail

      • getPluginFilter

        PluginFilter getPluginFilter()
        Returns currently installed plugin filter.
        返回当前安装的插件过滤器。
        Returns:
        installed plugin filter or null when no filter is installed. 已安装插件过滤器或未安装过滤器的情况。

      • setPluginFilter

        void setPluginFilter(PluginFilter filter)
        Sets a new plugin filter that will be used to decide which plugin is available for the current Browser instance. To remove filter and make all plugins available use setPluginFilter(null).
        设置一个新的插件过滤器，该过滤器将用于确定哪个插件可用于当前浏览器实例。要删除过滤器并使所有插件可用，请使用setPluginFilter（null）。
        Parameters:
        filter - the new plugin filter. Use null to remove filter. -新的插件过滤器。用于移除过滤器。

      • getPluginsInfo

        java.util.List<PluginInfo> getPluginsInfo()
        Returns a list with the information about installed plugins.
        返回包含有关已安装插件的信息的列表。
        Returns:
        a list with the information about installed plugins. 包含有关已安装插件的信息的列表。

      • isNPAPIPluginsSupported

        boolean isNPAPIPluginsSupported()
        Returns true if NPAPI plugins are supported.
        如果支持NPAPI插件，则返回true。
        Returns:
        true if NPAPI plugins are supported. 如果支持NPAPI插件。
